x|last=Strazzanti|num=40|pos=DB|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Thomas|last=Barber|num=41|pos=LB|class=SO}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Bailey|last=Schoenfelder|num=43|pos=LB|class=FR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Tommy|last=Fuller|num=44|pos=LB|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Carter|last=Coughlin|num=45|pos=LB|class=SO}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Winston|last=DeLattiboudere|num=46|pos=DL|class=SO|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Danny|last=Anderson|num=50|pos=DB|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Austin|last=Schirck|num=52|pos=DL|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Joe|last=Russell|num=57|pos=LB|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Connor|last=Novak-Goar|num=59|pos=DL|class=SO}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Boye|last=Mafe|num=69|pos=DL|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Malcolm|last=Robinson|num=75|pos=DL|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Sam|last=Renner|num=90|pos=DL|class=SO|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Noah|last=Hickcox|num=91|pos=DL|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Tai'yon|last=Devers|num=92|pos=DL|class=SO}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Merrick|last=Jackson|num=93|pos=DL|class=SR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Quinn|last=Coughlin|num=94|pos=DL|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Esezi|last=Otomewo|num=95|pos=DL|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Steven|last=Richardson|num=96|pos=DL|class=SR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Royal|last=Silver|num=97|pos=DL|class=JR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=O.J.|last=Smith|num=98|pos=DL|class=JR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Andrew|last=Stelter|num=99|pos=DL|class=SR}}\n|special_teams_players=\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Ryan|last=Santoso|num=18|pos=P|class=SR|rs=y|link=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Payton|last=Jordahl|num=25|pos=LS|class=JR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Grant|last=Ryerse|num=33|pos=K|pos2=P|class=FR}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Logan|last=McElfresh|num=34|pos=P|class=JR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Casey|last=O'Brien|num=36|pos=H|class=FR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=John|last=Mack|num=37|pos=K|class=FR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Emmit|last=Carpenter|num=38|pos=K|class=JR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Trey|last=Hansen|num=39|pos=LS|class=SO|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Justin|last=Juenemann|num=42|pos=K|class=SR|rs=y}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Jacob|last=Herbers|num=47|pos=P|class=SO|rs=y}}\n}}\n{{American football roster/Footer|roster_url=http://www.gophersports.com/sports/m-footbl/mtt/minn-m-footbl-mtt.html\n|accessdate=September 5, 2017\n|head_coach=\n* [[P. J. Fleck]] (Head Coach)\n|asst_coach=\n* [[Kirk Ciarrocca]] (Offensive Coordinator / Quarterbacks)\n* [[Robb Smith]] (Defensive Coordinator / Linebackers)\n* [[Kenni Burns]] (Running Backs)\n* Brian Callahan (Tight Ends)\n* Maurice Linguist (Defensive Backs)\n* [[Bryce Paup]] (Defensive Line)\n* Matt Simon (Wide Receivers)\n* [[Ed Warinner]] (Offensive Line / Run Game Coordinator)\n* Rob Wenger (Special Teams Coordinator)\n* Gerrit Chernoff (General Manager)\n* Dan Nichol (Head Strength & Conditioning)\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Minnesota Golden Gophers football navbox}}\n\n[[Category:2017 Big Ten Conference football season|Minnesota Golden Gophers football]]\n[[Category:Minnesota Golden Gophers football seasons]]\n[[Category:2017 in sports in Minnesota|Minnesota Golden Gophers]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American college football season}}\n{{Infobox NCAA team season\n|year = 2017\n|team = Minnesota Golden Gophers\n|sport = football\n|logo = Minnesota Golden Gophers logo.svg\n|logo_size = 125\n|logo_alt = \n|conference = Big Ten Conference\n|division = West Division\n|short_conf = Big Ten\n|CoachRank = \n|APRank = \n|CFPRank = \n|record = 5\u20137\n|conf_record = 2\u20137\n|head_coach = [[P. J. Fleck]]\n|hc_year= 1st\n|off_coach = [[Kirk Ciarrocca]]\n|oc_year = 1st\n|def_coach = [[Robb Smith]]\n|dc_year= 1st\n|off_scheme = \n|def_scheme = \n|stadium = [[TCF Bank Stadium]]<br>(Capacity: 50,805)\n|champion =\n|bowl = \n|bowl_result = \n}}\n{{2017 Big Ten football standings}}\nThe '''2017 Minnesota Golden Gophers football team''' represented the [[University of Minnesota]] during the [[2017 NCAA Division I FBS football season]]. The Gophers were led by first-year head coach [[P.J. Fleck]] and played their home games at [[TCF Bank Stadium]] in [[Minneapolis, Minnesota]]. Minnesota competed as a member of the West Division of the [[Big Ten Conference]]. They finished the season 5\u20137, 2\u20137 in Big Ten play to finish in sixth place in the West Division.\n\n==Recruiting==\n\n===Position key===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n|[[Running back|Back]]\n|'''B'''\n|rowSpan=\"6\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\"|\n|[[Center (American football)|Center]]\n|'''C'''\n|rowSpan=\"6\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\"|\n|[[Cornerback]]\n|'''CB'''\n|rowSpan=\"6\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\"|\n|[[Defensive back]]\n|'''DB'''\n|-\n|[[Defensive end]]\n|'''DE'''\n|[[Defensive lineman]]\n|'''DL'''\n|[[Defensive tackle]]\n|'''DT'''\n|[[End (American football)|End]]\n|'''E'''\n|-\n|[[Fullback (American football)|Fullback]]\n|'''FB'''\n|[[Guard (American football)|Guard]]\n|'''G'''\n|[[Halfback (American football)|Halfback]]\n|'''HB'''\n|[[Placekicker|Kicker]]\n|'''K'''\n|-\n|[[Kickoff returner]]\n|'''KR'''\n|[[Offensive tackle]]\n|'''OT'''\n|[[Lineman (American football)|Offensive lineman]]\n|'''OL'''\n|[[Linebacker]]\n|'''LB'''\n|-\n|[[Long snapper]]\n|'''LS'''\n|[[Punter (American football)|Punter]]\n|'''P'''\n|[[Punt returner]]\n|'''PR'''\n|[[Quarterback